    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <div class="aboutme">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p class="about-paragraph">
          I am currently a dental hygienist and studying Digital Media. I love
          throwing pottery and reading. I also spend a surprising amount of time
          telling my patients about Maine and all the great places to see and
          eat. I would love to share them with you in the hope that you can
          escape this humid place—even if just for a weekend.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pottery-image">
        <img
          src="images/potteryphoto.jpg"
          alt="Pottery Photo"
          class="pottery-photo"
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="project-section">
      <h3>My Emotional Support State</h3>
      <h4>There are MANY reasons I love Maine</h4>
      <ul class="like-list">
        <li>Average summmer weather is in the 70s</li>
        <li>Four seasons, who doesn't love apple picking!</li>
        <li>Ocean, mountians and islands</li>
        <li>The best lobster and ice cream</li>
      </ul>

      <a href="https://shainsofmaine.com/food-menu/"_blank"
        >Click Here for Shain's of Maine. This is my favorite place to eat!</a
